ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert udp $HOME_NET any -> any 53 ( msg:"INDICATOR-COMPROMISE Suspicious .pw dns query"; flow:to_server; content:!"|01|u|02|pw"; content:"|01 00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00 00|",depth 10,offset 2; content:"|02|pw|00|",distance 0,fast_pattern; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop,policy security-ips drop; service:dns; classtype:misc-activity; sid:28039; rev:7; )
